{"tid":254034,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[a酸] 服完療程去完問題","createTime":"2017-05-23T00:46:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T10:55:02.000Z","uid":69991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ab76e8ad120602502818591d9d811e876d5cb2a5","tid":254034,"uid":69991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T00:46:43.000Z","msg":"小弟仲有半個月就完全6個月療程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但塊面有好多印<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問各位好似我咁既巴絲打用咩方法去印<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbe6be097122845496301153a1a9dfb558662c04","tid":254034,"uid":69991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T00:53:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eee5faaa1a6b39fb77f14af486d26eeed5bf388","tid":254034,"uid":21292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T01:01:18.000Z","msg":"搭單問巴打你有冇爆發期？<br />\n我食a 酸到後期，面同頸生勁密集但唔大粒既瘡，醫生話唔係暗瘡黎，要停a 酸等d 瘡退左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我未試過生到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e7d59ed829ff6345c5290f5e8f1592516973fe1","tid":254034,"uid":69991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T01:29:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭單問巴打你有冇爆發期？<br />\n我食a 酸到後期，面同頸生勁密集但唔大粒既瘡，醫生話唔係暗瘡黎，要停a 酸等d 瘡退左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我未試過生到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我有爆發期呀 頭1,2個月都keep 住生。<br />\n之後三月打後就開始無乜。<br />\n然後4月開始無晒但我唔知係咪狂食1辣野熱氣野 keep住有一兩粒但係一日就謝果啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw, 巴打加油 好快就無晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01294ea9edff839b779f0143b4855a0006b0ea17","tid":254034,"uid":69991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T10:55:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}